    "license": "Free to use",
    "reference": "Gierk B, Kohlmann S, Kroenke K, et al. The Somatic Symptom Scale-8 (SSS-8): A brief measure of somatic symptom burden. JAMA Intern Med. 2014;174(3):399-407.",
    "instruction": "在过去7天里，以下各项症状对您的困扰程度如何？请选择最符合的选项。",
